<html metal:use-macro="here/main_template/macros/master" i18n:domain="noetique">

  <metal:main fill-slot="main">
    <style>
        .row {
        background-color: #EEE;
        padding: 1rem;
        }
    </style>

    <section id="noetique-section-agenda" tal:define="events view/next_events">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Rendez-vous publics</h2>
        <article tal:define="events view/next_events" tal:repeat="event events" class="card">
          <a href="${event/url}">
            <h3>${event/title}</h3>
            <span class="pat-moment" data-pat-moment="format:Do MMMM YYYY;">${event/start}</span>
              -
            <span>${event/location}</span>
            <p>${event/description}</p>
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="noetique-section-thoughts" tal:define="thoughts view/last_thoughts">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Journal philosophique au quotidien</h2>
        <footer>
          <a href="journal">Tout le journal</a>
        </footer>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="noetique-section-articles" tal:define="articles view/last_articles">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Ce que j'ai à dire au monde sur le monde</h2>
        <footer>
          <a href="journal">Tous les articles</a>
        </footer>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="noetique-section-books" tal:define="books view/last_books">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Mes derniers livres</h2>
        <article class="card" tal:repeat="book books">
          <a href="${book/url}">
            <img tal:attributes="src string:${book/url}/@@images/cover/mini" />
            <h5>${book/title}</h5>
          </a>
          <strong>Auteur</strong> : ${book/author}
          <br />
          <strong>Editeur</strong> : ${book/publisher}
          <br />
          <strong>Année</strong> : ${book/year}
        </article>
        <footer>
          <a href="livres">Tous les ouvrages</a>
        </footer>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="noetique-section-videos">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Vous préférez en images</h2>
        <article class="card">
          <!--<iframe frameborder="0" allowfullscreen width="100%" tal:attributes="src string:https://www.youtube.com/embed/${video/video_id}"></iframe>-->
        </article>
        <footer>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCplO3-iuNvhEinVj8Sxh6XA">Chaîne Youtube de Marc Halévy</a>
        </footer>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="noetique-section-services">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Puis-je vous aider ?</h2>
        <p class="h4">Services aux dirigeants, experts et penseurs</p>
        <div class="card-group">
          <article class="card">
Donec ullamcorper nulla non metus auctor fringilla. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus. Aenean lacinia bibendum nulla sed consectetur.
          </article>
          <article class="card">
Donec ullamcorper nulla non metus auctor fringilla. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus. Aenean lacinia bibendum nulla sed consectetur.
          </article>
          <article class="card">
